        <item>
            <title>Switch 2 玛利欧赛车世界，新赛场、新玩法与角色阵容抢先曝光</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/18/mariokartworld/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mariokartworld</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/18/mariokartworld/game-channel/#respond</comments>
