                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 18 Apr 2025 06:38:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nintendo Switch 2]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1304123</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂计划于 2025 年 6 月 5 日同步推出新主机 Nintendo Switch 2 与全新游戏《玛利欧赛车，世界》，游戏设计以「全球一体」为主轴，带来前所未见的连贯世界观。玩家可在城市、海洋、雪山与沙漠间自由驰骋，并透过连线功能展开最多 24 人的跨洲竞赛。同时，游戏亦将支援游戏语音通话与拍照分享等新功能，并加入多项辅助模式，令不同程度玩家都能轻松享受赛车乐趣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot.jpg"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304161" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1638screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>游戏世界采用无缝连接设计，所有赛道均建构于一个巨大世界地图内，让玩家从一条赛道自然驶入下一段旅程。新加入的世界赛道包括「玛利欧兄弟赛道」、「奖杯城市」、「盐味镇」、「罗洁塔天文台」、「鬼影电影院」等地点，赛道横跨高楼城市、河道水都、荒野弯道与幽暗森林。官方同时安排多条经典赛道回归，如「奇诺比奥工厂」、「碧姬海滩」、「瓦利欧船舰」等。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot.jpg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304129" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct249screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot.jpeg"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304130" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct141screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304131" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct150screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304132" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct20screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304133" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct221screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304134" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct27screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304135" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct237screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>角色方面，玩家除可选用玛利欧、路易吉、碧姬、库巴等熟面孔外，今集亦加入全新角色，例如「栗宝宝」、「加邦」与「乳牛」，每位角色配合不同车辆配置会带来独特性能组合，让玩家自由搭配出最合适组合。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304143" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct312screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304144" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct318screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304137" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct320screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304136" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct38screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304139" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct35screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304140" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct259screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304141" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct324screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304142" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct343screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>游戏主要分为两大赛事系统：「大奖赛」与「生存赛」。大奖赛包含「蘑菇杯」、「火焰花杯」、「星星杯」等级别，每组需完成 4 条赛道并累计排名。而生存赛则属连续长距离挑战模式，举行地点遍布整个游戏世界，赛道中设有淘汰制度，若未能于指定名次内通过检查点便会被剔除出局。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304145" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct429screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304146" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct419screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>道具设计仍为比赛逆转关键，游戏中将提供多款全新装备，包括可掉落金币的「黄金龟壳」、让对手结冰打滑的「冰冻花」、可变大碾压敌手的「巨大蘑菇」、能跳跃闪避攻击的「羽毛」、以及神秘魔法效果的「卡美克」。道具影响大，玩家需灵活运用，逆转局势。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304147" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct639screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304148" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct650screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304149" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct715screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304150" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct713screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304151" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct79screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304152" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct71screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>任天堂亦为新手玩家加入多项辅助模式，例如「方向盘辅助」可避免驶离赛道、「体感陀螺仪模式」可利用 Joy-Con 倾斜进行操控。此外，「蓄力跳跃」功能可于直线行驶时按住 R 键蓄力，放开时角色便会高跳，有助避开陷阱或越过障碍，甚至可瞬间切入捷径。</p><p>单人模式方面加入「倒转」功能，玩家可于操作失误时将个人时间倒回重试，惟其他赛车手仍会照常行驶，形成真实压力挑战。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304153" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct740screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304154" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct737screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>多人模式设计进一步升级，单机最多支援 4 人分割画面，而连线功能则容许最多 8 台 Switch 2 主机连线进行最多 24 人对战。玩家可以透过游戏聊天功能语音沟通，也可利用 Nintendo Switch 2 新增的摄影机实时观看对方表情，一台摄影机最多辨识 4 人脸部，增强互动趣味。</p><p>游戏还设有「时间挑战赛」、「团队对战」、「VS 模式」与「对战模式」等多元玩法，当中包括气球对战与金币争夺战等娱乐型比赛模式，满足不同游戏喜好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304155" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1046screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304156" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1152screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304157" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct117screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>在自由驾驶模式中，玩家可随意游览世界各地场景，并可于旅途中进行拍照、摆姿势、加入相框，记录赛事精彩瞬间。这个世界亦设有「P 开关」任务点，触发后会出现隐藏面板与金币，为探索旅程增添挑战。</p><p>游戏世界亦设有「耀西快餐」据点，玩家可外带「冲刺美食」，并有机会换取与料理相关的服装，自由搭配角色造型，为游戏加入生活感与乐趣。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304158" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1534screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304159" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1510screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1304160" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot-694x390.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot-694x390.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/direct1336screenshot.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>任天堂将推出主机与游戏同捆包，《玛利欧赛车，世界》预计与 Nintendo Switch 2 同日发售，为全球玩家展开一场跨地域、超规模的赛车盛典。</p><br /><b>
]]>
