            <title>iPhone + Mac 生态圈 AirDrop 以外的两机互动方法  10 个你可能忽略小贴士</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/17/iphone-with-mac/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-with-mac</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/04/17/iphone-with-mac/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 17 Apr 2025 11:18:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MAC App]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1302503</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>不少人爱用 Apple，不仅因为其产品规格、性能和设计，更因为其强大的生态系统——iPhone、iPad、Mac 甚至 Vision Pro 之间的无缝互通。这种互通让 Apple 产品成为「用过就回不去」的存在！虽然 AirDrop 是大家熟知的分享工具，但 Apple 生态还有更多实用功能，可能你还没发现！以下整合了 10 个超实用的生态技巧，让你的 iPhone、iPad 和 Mac 配合更高效。</p><h2>预先设定：</h2><p>要启用下面介绍的功能，首先你需要确保：</p><p>iPhone 和 Mac 登入相同 Apple ID；</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651238.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲需为同一 AppleID</p><p>iPhone 和 Mac 均连接到同一 Wi-Fi 网络；</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/2025041651249.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲连接至同一 Wi-Fi 网络</p><p>两边均已开启「接手」（Handoff）功能。</p><p>iPhone 开启接手功能步骤如下：<br />
首先开启「设定」，选择「一般」，点击「AirPlay 与接续互通」，开启「接手」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_1.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启 iPhone 接手功能</p><p>macOS 设定如下：</p><p>开启「设定」，选择「一般」，点击「AirDrop 与接手」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303680" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1-694x471.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="471" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1-694x471.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_2-1.jpg 700w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「AirDrop 与接手」</p><p>开启「允许在 Mac 和你的 iCloud 装置之间使用『接手』功能」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303679" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1-694x436.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="436" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1-694x436.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_3-1.jpg 704w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启「允许在 Mac 和你的 iCloud 装置之间使用『接手』功能」</p><h2>1. 通用剪贴板：跨装置复制贴上</h2><p>完成预先设定后，现在你可以在 iPhone 上复制文字、图片或连结，然后直接在 Mac 上贴上，反之亦然。例如你可以在 Mac Safari 上复制网址，然后直接在手机「贴上」，随即可在手机上继续阅读 Mac 上分享的网页。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303673" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4-694x279.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="279" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4-694x279.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_4.jpg 1252w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在 Mac 上复制网址</p><p>现在即可直接在 iPhone 贴上刚才复制的连结。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1303676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5-536x580.jpg" alt="" width="536" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5-536x580.jpg 536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/ios_5.jpg 832w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 536px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可直接分享 Mac 上复制的连结</p><p>你也可以从 iPhone 复制文字，然后直接在 Mac 贴上。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
